// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2625 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 6a90bd71-6c1a-55dc-a1f0-19d136022812

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *amazonlinux:1* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6* OR ImageFileName = *ubuntu:12.04*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
